window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Galaxyâ€™s Edge returns with an all-new adrenaline-fueled season of the military sci-fi series!</b></p> <p>With his duty to the Legion satisfied, Wraith sets out to find a lost member of his crew - the young girl Prisma. Not only does the journey bring with it more death and destruction - and loss - than he ever imagined, it revives the shadows of a forgotten past. The only way forward is to follow the footsteps of the legendary Tyrus Rechs.</p> <p>Meanwhile, as the galaxy struggles to steady itself following the fall of a corrupt and bloated republic, dangerous threats vie for power. Insidious deep-state operatives, vicious abominations pulled from forbidden savage technology...and something impossibly ancient, awakening at long last to emerge from the darkness between the stars.</p>"; 
